&none      &kp CARET  &kp AT     &kp HASH   &kp DLLR   &kp PRCNT                                                                &none      &none       &none        &none      &none      &none
&kp EXCL   &kp LBRC   &kp LPAR   &kp RPAR   &kp RBRC   &kp BSLH                                                                 &none      &kp DEL     &kp LS(TAB)  &none      &none      &none
&kp GRAVE  &kp PIPE   &kp STAR   &kp EQUAL  &kp UNDER  &kp AMPS                                                                 &kp QMARK  &kp BSPC    &kp TAB      &kp SPACE  &kp ENTER  &none
&none      &kp LT     &kp TILDE  &kp MINUS  &kp GT     &kp SLASH  &mt LGUI PRCNT  &kp LCTRL  &kp LALT   &trans  &trans  &trans  &kp SEMI   &kp COLON   &kp COMMA    &kp DOT    &none      &none
